  "translations": {
    "en": "I asked him about the woman who sees blood before her regular time of menstruation. So he said: When she sees blood before her regular time of menstruation, let her abandon salat, for perhaps the time has come early for her. So if it is more than her days in which she used to menstruate, let her wait three days after her days have passed. Then if she has waited three days and the blood has not stopped from her, let her do as the woman with istihadha does.",
